00:19:47.603 --> 00:19:49.229
Kau suka ubi manis, 'kan?

00:20:16.006 --> 00:20:18.634
- [Yong-sik, berbisik] Abaikan.
- [Geum-ja] Sudah, tak usah.

00:20:21.595 --> 00:20:23.096
